rows.label: qst202410_0010
rows.name: Wow, they're really worked up...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0020
rows.name:
Everyone really liked
the songstress's song.

rows.label: qst202410_0030
rows.name:
We were all excited about making
that Nopon our Kountess.

rows.label: qst202410_0040
rows.name: Are you okay with that...?[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0050
rows.name: Even though we found the real Kountess.

rows.label: qst202410_0060
rows.name:
Oh! I can't believe you
found the real one!

rows.label: qst202410_0070
rows.name:
Thank you, heroes! You
have saved our Kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0080
rows.name:
Well, I wouldn't say "saved." She
seemed to be having a good time...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0090
rows.name:
If anything, it felt like we
were dragging her away...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0100
rows.name: Modesty, modesty.

rows.label: qst202410_0110
rows.name:
Come, you too must celebrate
the return of the Kountess.

rows.label: qst202410_0120
rows.name: We can eat delicious food for free, mo!

rows.label: qst202410_0130
rows.name:
I wonder if they'll have all-you-can-eat
Juicy Samod, my favorite.

rows.label: qst202410_0140
rows.name:
No, no, that's not your
favorite, Ibuki...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0150
rows.name: Then, was it Cream Orange Paratha?

rows.label: qst202410_0160
rows.name: That's my favorite.

rows.label: qst202410_0170
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Anyway, let's take them
up on their offer.

rows.label: qst202410_0180
rows.name: Hey...[ML:Dash ] Where's Ibuki?

rows.label: qst202410_0190
rows.name:
Hmm? She was right beside
me a moment ago...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0200
rows.name:
Now, let me reintroduce
the real Kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0210
rows.name: The one here is our Tirkin Kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0220
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Eh?

rows.label: qst202410_0230
rows.name: The Kountess is safe!

rows.label: qst202410_0240
rows.name: So lively, so lively!

rows.label: qst202410_0250
rows.name: Why is Ibuki up there...?[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0260
rows.name: Hey, Ibuki! You're not the Kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0270
rows.name: It's me, Ibuki! I'm doing great!

rows.label: qst202410_0280
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Oooooh!

rows.label: qst202410_0290
rows.name: That one is not the Kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0300
rows.name: The Tirkin Kountess is me!

rows.label: qst202410_0310
rows.name: Kountess?

rows.label: qst202410_0320
rows.name:
There are two Kountesses!
Which one is the Kountess?

rows.label: qst202410_0330
rows.name: Is that the Kountess?

rows.label: qst202410_0340
rows.name: No, that little one is the Kountess.

rows.label: qst202410_0350
rows.name: Lots of Kountesses?

rows.label: qst202410_0360
rows.name: Lots of Kountesses.

rows.label: qst202410_0370
rows.name:
No, the one on the right is
obviously the Kountess...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0380
rows.name: Everyone, quiet down!

rows.label: qst202410_0390
rows.name: The Kountesses have...[ML:Dash ] multiplied.

rows.label: qst202410_0400
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Ooooooooh!

rows.label: qst202410_0410
rows.name: This is great, this is great!

rows.label: qst202410_0420
rows.name: Great, great!

rows.label: qst202410_0430
rows.name:
I am the Kountess! There
is only one Kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0440
rows.name: Everyone, rejoice!

rows.label: qst202410_0450
rows.name:
So many Kountesses! The
Tirkin tribe is safe!

rows.label: qst202410_0460
rows.name: The Tirkin tribe is the best!

rows.label: qst202410_0470
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Oooooh!

rows.label: qst202410_0480
rows.name: They seem really excited, mo...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0490
rows.name: This is getting out of hand...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0500
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]Ah, I remember now.

rows.label: qst202410_0510
rows.name:
All Tirkin are bird-brains. They'd
forget about me right away...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0520
rows.name: That's why I ran away from home...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0530
rows.name: There, there. It's okay, it's okay.

rows.label: qst202410_0540
rows.name:
The Kountess and Ibuki are friends,
so Ibuki will explain everything.

rows.label: qst202410_0550
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]Ibiki... Ibiki, thank you.

rows.label: qst202410_0560
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]It's not Ibiki, it's
Ibuki, Omuel-Emuel-chan.

rows.label: qst202410_0570
rows.name: Wrong. I am Emulomuel.

rows.label: qst202410_0580
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Was that it? Hmm, Tirkin
names are difficult.

rows.label: qst202410_0590
rows.name:
But I've remembered it now, so
it's okay, Emul-Emuol-chan.

rows.label: qst202410_0600
rows.name: Wrong, Fubuki. I am Emulomuel.

rows.label: qst202410_0610
rows.name:
It's not Fubuki, it's Ibuki. Remember
it properly, Omuel-Emuol-chan.

rows.label: qst202410_0620
rows.name:
Wrong, wrong. Hibiki,
remember it properly!

rows.label: qst202410_0630
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Oooooh!

rows.label: qst202410_0640
rows.name:
Is that comedy routine all
setup, no punchline...?[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202410_0650
rows.name:
I wonder when it will end...[ML:Dash ]
I really hate it when
there's no punchline...[ML:Dash ]
